  "title": {
   "en": "Oukakoku Koukyuu no Kusushi"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "ja": "旺華国後宮の薬師"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "The best medicine is one that is not bitter and is easy for anyone to take.\n\nEi Rin (Ying Ling) is a court lady who aspires to become a doctor. One day, when she begins selling medicinal tea in the imperial palace, she is summoned by the emperor, who is interested in her unusual formula. He asks her to make a bitter medicine easier to take for his sweet-tooth, and she is appointed as the emperor's personal doctor She is joyous that the emperor has taken a liking to her formula, however, it is short-lived when she is told that she will be promoted to the position of empress. \n\n\"My goal is not to be a empress, but a doctor!\"",
   "ja": "『不苦の良薬』――苦くない、誰でも飲みやすい良薬こそ至高。後宮の官女・英鈴は、そう志して女だてらに薬師を目指している。ある日、後宮で薬茶を売り始めると、珍しい処方に興味を持った皇帝から呼び出される。すると、「甘党の余のために、苦い薬を飲みやすくしてほしい」と、皇帝専属のお薬係に任命された。処方を気に入られた喜びも束の間、妃に昇格すると言われてしまい……？「私が目指しているのは、妃ではなく薬師です！」皇帝のお気に入りが「おいしい処方」を掲げて活躍する、中華おくすり物語！"
  },
